<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA20">
<l>aṟivāṉun tāṉē yaṟivippāṉ ṟāṉē</l>
<l>yaṟivā yaṟikiṉṟāṉ ṟāṉē - yaṟikiṉṟa</l>
<l>meypporuḷun tāṉē viricuṭarpā rākāya</l>
<l>mapporuḷun tāṉē yavaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the one who will know. He is the one who makes know.</l>
<l>He is the one who knows, being knowledge. He is the true</l>
<l>meaning that is known. Expansive light, earth, ether,</l>
<l>it is that matter that is him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
